text: Hylte/Halmstad VBK is a volleyball club in Hyltebruk, Sweden. It was established in 1980. The club won the Swedish men's national championship in the years of 1995, 1996 2000, 2001, 2005, 2006, 2013 and 2018. The women's team won the Swedish national championship in 2014. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1980 establishments in Sweden Category:Volleyball clubs in Sweden
